            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>晟鈦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3229:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3229\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3229-TW</a>)17日09:46上漲2.75元，股價漲停報30.7元，委買5,967張，成交428張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為印刷電路板之製造加工及買賣。磷銅球之製造加工及買賣。鑽孔代工業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>晟鈦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3229:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3229\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3229-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲49.07%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲6.51%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+230 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+136 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+94 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
